All snack board enthusiasts know: a balance of sweet and savory is key! We whipped up a seasonal snack board with @cafigs and Feedfeed’s @clarelangan. 
👉 Did you know California Fresh Fig season is now thru November? When you see them, buy them! Find @cafigs near you by visiting your local grocery retailer. 
👉 Want more fig inspo? Check out our Fig Feed! https://thefeedfeed.com/figs and follow @cafigs #feedfeed #figs

node.text:
Use @filippoberio_us for all of your baking needs (#ad)! Heart-healthy #FilippoBerio Olive Oil takes butter’s place, which is what’s traditionally used in pie dough, for these Balsamic, Blackberry, and Ricotta Hand Pies. The olive oil sub along with the use of #vegan ricotta cheese makes this a #dairyfree treat! The recipe makes 8 of the cutest personal pies, perfect for summer picnics and days outdoors.

👉Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/fb-handpies #feedfeed #oliveoil #hearthealthy #pie #feedfeed #blackberry #baking #smallbatch
